description: [``botocore``] Added support for encryption in transit for Memcached clusters. Customers can now launch Memcached cluster with encryption in transit enabled when using Memcached version 1.6.12 or later.
[``botocore``] New APIs for Monitor that help you understand how your predictors perform over time.
[``botocore``] Adding modelMetrics as part of DescribeRecommender API response for Personalize.
